body: > [!IMPORTANT] > Fix frontend exception by changing `input` and `output` fields from `null` to `undefined` across multiple components and updating JSON handling logic. > > - **Behavior**: > - Change `input` and `output` fields from `string | null` to `string | undefined` in `ObservationTree`, `TracePreview`, `TraceTimelineView`, `index.tsx`, `JumpToPlaygroundButton`, `NewDatasetItemFromObservationButton`, `observations.ts`, and `traces.ts`. > - Update JSON stringification logic in `observations.ts` and `traces.ts` to handle `undefined` values. > - **Components**: > - Update `IOTableCell` in `CodeJsonViewer.tsx` to handle `undefined` data. > - Modify `parseGeneration` in `JumpToPlaygroundButton.tsx` to handle `undefined` `input` and `output`. > - **Misc**: > - Adjust `Trace` and `Observation` types to reflect changes in `input` and `output` handling. > > This description was created by [](https://www.ellipsis.dev?ref=langfuse%2Flangfuse&utm_source=github&utm_medium=referral) for 6b2548a384887a63e29cf64c17189a4fb1e6f2a8.
